---
title: BBQ Dry-Rub Chicken with Corn and Ranch Dressing
description: Summer is perfect for a family BBQ! Enjoy BBQ-rubbed chicken, corn and golden roasted potatoes! You'll never want butter on corn again after you try it slathered in ranch dressing!
